</head>

<body>
    <div id="docu-alert">
        <div class="alert-header">
           !! 警告 !! 警告 !!
        </div>
        <div id="alert-body-1">
            <section>检测到未授权访问</section>
            <section>错误  错误  错误  错误  错误</section>
            <section>检-检-检---▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓</section>
        </div>
        <div id="alert-body-2">
            授权批准。
            十分感谢您，▓▓▓▓汉斯·阿尔普。⿂⿂⿂
        </div>
        <div id="alert-button">
            <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4485/offset/5">点击继续。</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="docuviewer">
            <div id="docu-header">
                    <span>基金会文档阅览器</span> <span>// 授</span><span>权内容</span>
            </div>
            <div id="docu-nav">
                <div id="back-button">
                    ◀
                </div>
                <div id="forward-button">
                    ▶
                </div>
            </div>    
            <div class="page-container">
            <div id="page1" class="active-page">
                <section>
                    <p>前与后</p>
                    <p>内和外</p>
                    <p>看上再看下</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p class="labeltext">理解是找出一个空杯子来喝空气</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">聆听是只有狗会从它们的专长中找出的特质</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">达达不见了。达达被找到。</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p>达达是繁琐无聊的教条焦林里升起的光</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <figure>
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/watchinglistening.png" type="image/png">
                            <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/watchinglistening.png" alt="不要看向别处。">
                        </picture>
                    </figure>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p class="labeltext">躲躲躲</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">它要找上你了</p>
                    <p>自满还有那粉碎你座下暗物质的东西</p>
                    <p>在恐怖与可爱中闪着</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-container">
            <div id="page2">
                <section>
                    <p class="labeltext">我坐在滴落着黑暗之质，脱下手套的正义之手的环抱中</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">在癌骨的裂缝中沉沦</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">踏上万物间翻腾的矛盾</p>
                    <p class="labeltext">喝下饮下再吐气</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p class="labeltext">在矛盾中我们找到了自己的全部</p>
                    <p>在矛盾中我们凝视着随视线破碎的重压</p>
                    <p>在矛盾中我们找到了<span class="larger">↴</span></p>
                    <p>我们找到了达达</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p>但已经无所谓了</p>
                    <p><span class="larger">非也</span>已经无所谓于是一切失去了意义</p>
                    <p>而一切对于我们关心的一切而言再无意义</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <figure>
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/watchingone.svg" type="image/svg">
                            <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/watchingone.svg" alt="上来吧，来看看你们颠倒的模样">
                        </picture>
                    </figure>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-container">
            <div id="page3">
                <section>
                    <p><span>摇 <span>影 <span>间 <span>乏 <span>味 <span>哭 <span>泣 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
                    <p class="labeltext">百闻不如一见：</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p>你</p>
                    <p>正在</p>
                    <p>躲藏</p>
                    <p>你</p>
                    <p>没有</p>
                    <p>品味</p>
                    <p>你</p>
                    <p>就是</p>
                    <p>本质</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <p>就像极简和繁琐<span>降生</span></p>
                    <p>之时的尖啸</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-container">
            <div id="page4">
                <section>
                    <p class="labeltext">我们在这里</p>
                    <p>我在这里</p>
                    <p>我是汉斯·阿尔普。</p>
                    <p>我们是汉斯·阿尔普。</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <figure>
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/HANSARP.svg" type="image/png">
                            <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Adark-light-4/HANSARP.svg" alt="我们就是我们">
                        </picture>
                    </figure>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        var page1 = document.getElementById("page1");

        var page1 = document.getElementById("page1");
        var page2 = document.getElementById("page2");
        var page3 = document.getElementById("page3");
        var page4 = document.getElementById("page4");

        var currentPage = 1;

        function duplicate() {
            var clone1 = page1.cloneNode(true); // "deep" clone
            var clone2 = page2.cloneNode(true); // "deep" clone
            var clone3 = page3.cloneNode(true); // "deep" clone
            var clone4 = page4.cloneNode(true); // "deep" clone
            clone1.id = "page1" + "-duplicate";
            clone2.id = "page2" + "-duplicate";
            clone3.id = "page3" + "-duplicate";
            clone4.id = "page4" + "-duplicate";
            // or clone.id = ""; if the divs don't need an ID
            page1.parentNode.appendChild(clone1);
            page2.parentNode.appendChild(clone2);
            page3.parentNode.appendChild(clone3);
            page4.parentNode.appendChild(clone4);
        }

        var backButton = document.getElementById("back-button");
        var forwardButton = document.getElementById("forward-button");

        backButton.addEventListener("click", function(){
            if (currentPage == 2) {
                currentPage = 1;
                page2.classList.remove("active-page");
                page1.classList.add("active-page");
            }
            else if (currentPage == 3) {
                currentPage = 2;
                page3.classList.remove("active-page");
                page2.classList.add("active-page");
            }
            else if (currentPage == 4) {
                currentPage = 3;
                page4.classList.remove("active-page");
                page3.classList.add("active-page");
            }
        }, false);

        forwardButton.addEventListener("click", function(){
            if (currentPage == 1) {
                currentPage = 2;
                page1.classList.remove("active-page");
                page2.classList.add("active-page");
            }
            else if (currentPage == 2) {
                currentPage = 3;
                page2.classList.remove("active-page");
                page3.classList.add("active-page");
            }
            else if (currentPage == 3) {
                currentPage = 4;
                page3.classList.remove("active-page");
                page4.classList.add("active-page");
                setTimeout(function(){
                    var page4Duplicate = document.getElementById("page4-duplicate");
                    page4.classList.add("overlay");
                    page4Duplicate.classList.add("overlay");
                }, 3000);
                setTimeout(function(){
                    var docuviewer = document.getElementById("docuviewer");
                    var alert = document.getElementById("docu-alert");
                    docuviewer.classList.add("darken");
                    setTimeout(function(){
                        var alertBody1 = document.getElementById("alert-body-1");
                        var alertBody2 = document.getElementById("alert-body-2");
                        var alertButton = document.getElementById("alert-button");
                        alert.classList.add("alert-active");
                        alertBody1.classList.add("alert-body-show");
                        setTimeout(function(){
                            alertBody1.classList.add("overlay");
                            setTimeout(function(){
                                alertBody1.classList.remove("overlay");
                                alertBody1.classList.remove("alert-body-show");
                                alertBody2.classList.add("alert-body-show");
                                setTimeout(function(){
                                    alertButton.classList.add("alert-body-show");
                                },250);
                            },500);
                        },1500);
                    }, 1500);
                }, 3500);
            }
        },false);

        window.fitText( document.getElementById("docu-header"),2.5 );
    </script>
</body>
